text: Jaroslav Starosta (born 21 April 1937) is a Czech rower who represented Czechoslovakia. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics in Rome with the men's coxless four where they came fourth. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Czechoslovak male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague Category:Rowers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
